Key Match Events: Daz Cameron, Max Schuemann, and Nick Allen executed a bunt-fueled rally in the 12th inning to score two runs, securing the Athletics' 4-3 win over the Astros.
Jose Altuve opened the bottom of the 12th with an RBI double, but the Astros couldn't capitalize, while the Athletics' pitching held them to a 3-4 deficit.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Athletics improved to 63-82 with the win, while the Astros dropped to 77-67.
